    public static class Videobridge.Statistics

    Basic statistics/metrics about the videobridge like cumulative/total number of channels created, cumulative/total number of channels failed, etc.

        public java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicLong totalLossDegradedParticipantMs
        The total number of participant-milliseconds that are loss-degraded on this Videobridge. We chose the unit to be millis because we expect that a lot of our calls spend very few ms (<500) in the lossDegraded state for example, and they might get cut to 0.
